text: The 1994 Russian Figure Skating Championships () took place in Saint Petersburg. Skaters competed in the disciplines of men's singles, ladies' singles, pair skating, and ice dancing. The results were one of the criteria used to pick the Russian teams to the 1994 World Championships and the 1994 European Championships. ==Senior results== ===Men=== {| class="wikitable" |- ! Rank !
